content: संपत् {c1c} <ab>P.</ab> {@--1@} To fly or meet together, assemble. {@--2@} To go or roam about. {@--3@} To attack, fall upon, assail. {@--4@} To come to pass, occur, happen. {@--5@} To fall down, alight, fly down. {%--<ab>Caus.</ab>%} {@--1@} To bring near. {@--2@} To collect or assemble together, bring or call together. {@--3@} To throw down, cast, hurl down.
